      ASSIGN <change>-instances->* TO FIELD-SYMBOL(<instances>).
      me->written = <instances>.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.

  METHOD if_abap_behavior_testdouble~read.
    LOOP AT retrievals ASSIGNING FIELD-SYMBOL(<retrieval>).
